</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="723" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="15.[95,1301,1514,2257]" pageId="15" pageNumber="723">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[95,329,1868,1901]" pageId="15" pageNumber="723">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Red-hipped Squirrel is almost entirely terrestrial and is recorded as being fairly inactive during the winter season.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
