</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="723" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="15.[95,1301,1514,2257]" pageId="15" pageNumber="723">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[98,448,2030,2059]" pageId="15" pageNumber="723">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Redhipped Squirrel has a wide distribution, a presumed large population, and occurs in a number ofprotected areas. It has been regionally Red Listed in China as Near Threatened.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
